api.options

Class AfterOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.options.AbstractOption
      • api.options.AbstractParameteredOption<Long>
        • api.options.AfterOption

  • public class AfterOption
extends AbstractParameteredOption<Long>
    The BeforeOption class represents the after option several commands have. Timestamps are passed with data type long. Whenever the word parameter is used within the documentation of this option, the option's parameter is referred to, not the method's one.
    Author:
    Loris
